title: The strangest iceberg I've ever looked at...

media:group.media:title: The strangest iceberg I've ever looked at...
media:group.media:description:
We’re going to be taking a look at this iceberg which has no title, no category, it’s just… it’s the strangest iceberg I’ve ever looked at. I don’t quite remember how I found it, but it’s been sitting on my phone for almost a year now and I thought it was time to bring it out and show it to the world. So sit back and relax as I take you through the strangest iceberg I’ve ever looked at.
